      <title>刚果将 Tenke 的铜出售给三家重量级交易商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/congo-sells-copper-from-tenke-to-trio-of-trading-heavyweights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc)、摩科瑞能源集团 (Mercuria Energy Group) 和托克集团 (Trafigura Group) 正在从刚果民主共和国的国有矿业公司购买铜，这是该公司首次销售来自合资项目的金属。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/congo-sells-copper-from-tenke-to-trio-of-trading-heavyweights</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗认为一些科技公司今年仍在考虑在美国上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/citi-sees-some-tech-companies-still-weighing-us-ipos-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团一位高级银行家表示，一些科技公司正考虑在今年最后三个月在美国交易所上市，这加剧了潜在的 IPO 需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/citi-sees-some-tech-companies-still-weighing-us-ipos-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:16:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通等多家银行正在为英国公司 Belron 处理超过 80 亿欧元的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/belron-set-to-launch-over-8-billion-in-debt-for-refinancing-and-dividend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，摩根大通、法国巴黎银行和美国银行等银行将向英国汽车玻璃维修和更换公司 Belron 发行超过 80 亿欧元（88 亿美元）的债券，所得款项将用于延长债务到期日和为股东分红提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/belron-set-to-launch-over-8-billion-in-debt-for-refinancing-and-dividend</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国能源信息署最新预测称，2024 年美国石油需求将稳定下来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/us-oil-demand-to-plateau-in-2024-eia-says-in-latest-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国能源信息署称，预计今年美国石油需求增长将趋于平稳，这是市场最新的看跌指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/us-oil-demand-to-plateau-in-2024-eia-says-in-latest-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:02:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者大批撤离导致 Wamco 关键债券基金规模缩水至 150 亿美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/investor-exodus-shrinks-wamco-key-bond-fund-to-under-15-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者赎回潮，西方资产管理公司 (Western Asset Management Co.) 的旗舰核心加债券基金规模缩水至 150 亿美元以下，今年迄今已缩水逾三分之一，原因是该公司资深交易员兼联席首席投资官肯·利奇 (Ken Leech) 受到联邦政府调查，客户纷纷撤资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/investor-exodus-shrinks-wamco-key-bond-fund-to-under-15-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:59:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德的 Hyler 认为房地产市场在经历两年低迷后将回暖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brookfield-s-hyler-sees-thaw-in-real-estate-after-two-year-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司表示，随着经济状况好转，房地产市场正在反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brookfield-s-hyler-sees-thaw-in-real-estate-after-two-year-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国开始出售德国商业银行股份，首席执行官宣布离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/commerzbank-ceo-flags-departure-as-germany-starts-to-sell-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行首席执行官曼弗雷德·诺夫 (Manfred Knof) 不会寻求延长合同，这使得该德国银行在政府开始出售其股份的同时寻找替代者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/commerzbank-ceo-flags-departure-as-germany-starts-to-sell-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通降低盈利乐观情绪，导致银行股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/jpmorgan-shares-slide-as-pinto-says-analysts-are-too-optimistic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司总裁丹尼尔平托表示，分析师对明年的支出和净利息收入的预测过于乐观，导致该行股价出现四年多来最大跌幅，引领银行股走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/jpmorgan-shares-slide-as-pinto-says-analysts-are-too-optimistic</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:28:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>转基因小麦开发商遭遇挫折 股价两年来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/world-s-first-gmo-wheat-gets-more-real-after-us-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于其突破性的转基因小麦种子遭遇挫折，阿根廷作物科技公司 Bioceres Crop Solutions SA 的股价有望创下两年来最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/world-s-first-gmo-wheat-gets-more-real-after-us-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
